<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Free U.S. tax calculators for income tax, state income tax, sales tax, self-employment tax, and capital gains tax.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="google-site-verification" content="TT2j7SgIafccBK-Nfk4ilXVIDXEJdSmyQJf2wL9QY0o" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-icon">💵</span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>

      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/income-tax-calculator">Income Tax</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content centered">
      <p class="eyebrow">Free U.S. Tax Calculators</p>
      <h1>Simple tax estimates start here</h1>
      <p>
        Free calculators for federal income tax, state tax, sales tax,
        self-employment tax, and capital gains planning.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="/income-tax-calculator">Calculate Income Tax</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="#state-calculators">View State Calculators</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="card-grid feature-grid">
      <a class="card feature-card" href="/income-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">📊</div>
        <h2>Income Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate federal taxable income, refund, amount owed, and effective tax rate.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/self-employment-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">🧾</div>
        <h2>Self-Employment Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate Social Security and Medicare tax for freelance, contractor, and gig income.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">📈</div>
        <h2>Capital Gains Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate short-term and long-term tax on stocks, crypto, real estate, or other asset sales.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/sales-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">🛒</div>
        <h2>Sales Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate sales tax, combined tax rate, discount amount, and final purchase total.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/payroll-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">💼</div>
        <h2>Payroll Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate paycheck withholding, Social Security, Medicare, state withholding, and net pay.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/california-income-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">🌉</div>
        <span class="badge">POPULAR</span>
        <h2>California Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate federal tax for California residents and prepare for state tax planning.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/texas-income-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">⭐</div>
        <h2>Texas Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate federal tax for Texas residents with no broad-based state income tax.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="card feature-card" href="/florida-income-tax-calculator">
        <div class="icon-box">☀️</div>
        <h2>Florida Tax</h2>
        <p>Estimate federal tax for Florida residents with no broad-based state income tax.</p>
        <span class="card-link">Start Calculating →</span>
      </a>
    </section>

        
    <section class="content" id="state-calculators">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow dark">All 50 States</p>
        <h2>State Income Tax Calculators</h2>
        <p>Choose your state to estimate federal tax and view state-specific tax calculator pages.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="state-list">
        <% states.forEach(function(state) { %>
          <a href="/<%= state.slug %>-income-tax-calculator"><%= state.name %></a>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content disclaimer-box">
      <h2>Tax estimate disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        MyTaxCalcs provides estimates for educational purposes only. It is not tax,
        legal, accounting, or financial advice. Consult a qualified tax professional
        before making tax decisions.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
    <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    <p>© 2026 MyTaxCalcs.com</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

